    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but i'm not talking about getting drunk or anything. just like, one glass of wine to help me unwind? i've heard some people say it actually helps the sedative work more smoothly so you don't feel as groggy the next morning. is it really that dangerous if it's just a tiny amount?",
